<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.7.6">
<l>āyiraṅ kuṉṟañ ceṉṟutok kaṉaiya vaṭalpurai yeḻiltikaḻ tiraṭōḷ</l>
<l>āyiran tuṇiya vaṭalmaḻup paṟṟi maṟṟava ṉakalvicum paṇaiya</l>
<l>vāyiram peyarā lamararceṉ ṟiṟaiñca vaṟituyi lalaikaṭal naṭuvē</l>
<l>yāyirañ cuṭarvā yaravaṇait tuyiṉṟā ṉaraṅkamā nakaramarn tāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one who lies calmly in the great city of Araṅkam is the one who sleeps</l>
<l rend="indent">on a bed that is a serpent with one-thousand fiery mouths,</l>
<l>In yogic repose amidst the crashing sea, as immortals, gathering,</l>
<l rend="indent">praise [him] with one-thousand names,</l>
<l>Since he, having grasped the battle axe, sundered</l>
<l rend="indent">one-thousand bulging shoulders, famed for their strength</l>
<l>And fit for battle, massing [and] falling like one-thousand mountains,</l>
<l rend="indent">so that his rival reached the sprawling heavens.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
